eliana@emacare.com

[Poor quality water caused by inadequate sewage systems in the setting of volatile political environments and displaced persons exacerbate the risk of cholera and other waterborne diseases. The flow of contaminated water across country borders can spread _Vibrio cholerae_ without the need of people. - Mod.LL

